@startuml
autonumber

title "System Sequence Diagram - US05: Build a Station (Happy Path)"


actor "Player" as Player
participant ":System" as System

activate Player

Player -> System: requests to access system
activate System
System --> Player: displays login screen
deactivate System

Player -> System: provides username and password
activate System
System --> Player: grants access to player interface
deactivate System



Player -> System: requests to see available maps

activate System
System --> Player: shows list of available maps
deactivate System

Player -> System: selects a map

activate System
System --> Player: loads and displays the selected map
deactivate System

Player -> System: asks to build a station

activate System
System --> Player: requests station type (DEPOT, STATION, TERMINAL)
deactivate System

Player -> System: selects station type

activate System
System --> Player: requests location (Position) on map for the station
deactivate System

Player -> System: provides location coordinates

activate System
alt station type is "STATION"
    System --> Player: requests center point selection (NE, SE, NW, SW)
    deactivate System

    Player -> System: selects center point
    activate System
end

System --> Player: proposes station name based on closest city
System --> Player: displays station cost and economic radius
System --> Player: shows preview of station placement and requests confirmation
deactivate System

Player -> System: confirms station placement

activate System
System --> Player: deducts cost from Player's budget
System --> Player: displays operation success
System --> Player: updates map with the new station
deactivate System

@enduml